<h1 >祭月</h1>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" href="javascript:;" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=1052346" target="_blank" class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" nslog-type="90000102"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num"></span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">古代对月神的祭祀。先秦已有此神祭祀活动,称为“夜明”或“夕月”。是中国炎黄子孙的重要团圆节日之一。</div><div class="para" label-module="para">在广东地区，人们有着在八月十五晚上祭<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%8B%9C%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%98">拜月娘</a>的习俗。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
祭月
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">定&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;义</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
古代对月神的祭祀
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">又称为</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
“夜明”或“夕月”<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%8B%9C%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%98">拜月娘</a>
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">时&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;间</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
在中秋夜
</dd>
</dl></div>
<div class="lemmaWgt-lemmaCatalog">
